title: THURSDAY 4/22 - IS JALEN HURTS THE STARTER IN PHILLY?
itunes:title: THURSDAY 4/22 - IS JALEN HURTS THE STARTER IN PHILLY?
description:
The Eagles traded away Carson Wentz, all but guaranteeing Jalen Hurts would be the starter, but head coach Nick Sirianni (0:06) not ready to make that claim yet. The Jaguars hold the first pick in the draft, but will they keep the pick? General Manager Trent Baalke says they've fielded calls about trading the pick (0:50). Former Ohio State QB Justin Fields revels he's been dealing with epilepsy (1:29)
